# 🎒 Campus Lost & Found Portal

A full-stack web application to help students report and find lost items within a campus.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 🔐 User Registration & Login
* 📦 Add Lost / Found Items
* 🖼 Upload Item Images
* 🔍 Search Items by Title
* 📍 View Item Details (Location, Description)
* 🙋 Claim Lost Items
* 🛠 Admin Panel:

  * Manage Items
  * Delete Items
  * Manage Users
  * Delete Users (Admin Protected)

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend

* HTML
* CSS (Bootstrap)
* JavaScript

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js

### Database

* MongoDB (Local / Atlas)

### Others

* Multer (Image Upload)
* CORS

---

